				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Light hydrocarbons are less dense crude oils with higher API gravity. They contain more light hydrocarbons and can be used in refineries to produce high-value products such as gasoline, diesel fuel, and jet fuel through simple distillation. They are categorized chemically as Alkanes or paraffins. Hydrocarbons are compounds comprised of hydrogen and carbon and can come in various forms such as gas, liquid, solid, or polymers.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">轻质碳氢化合物是密度较小、API 重力较高的原油。它们含有更多的轻烃，可用于炼油厂，通过简单蒸馏生产汽油、柴油和喷气燃料等高价值产品。它们在化学上被归类为烷烃或石蜡。碳氢化合物是由氢和碳组成的化合物，有气体、液体、固体或聚合物等多种形态。</common:generalComment>
